'''噬中齿鱼属'''（[[学名|学名]]：''Piranhamesodon''）是侏罗纪晚期（约1.52亿年前）的一属[[硬齿鱼目|硬齿鱼类]]。它在[[德国|德国]][[巴伐利亚州|巴伐利亚州]]的[[索伦霍芬|索伦霍芬]]组的Plattenkalk矿床中被发现。它以尖利的锯齿状牙齿而闻名，这让人联想到了[[食人鱼|食人鱼]]，这是一种非常不寻常的特征，因为硬齿鱼目中的大多数物种都以贝壳类动物为食，它们的牙齿扁平而破碎。它也是已知具有这种特征的最古老的[[硬骨鱼|硬骨鱼]]。这种不寻常的组合也反映在它的属名上，其由食人鱼和常见的硬齿鱼目属级分类群[[后缀树|后缀]]Mesodon组合而来。在同一地区发现的其他鱼类的化石上可能有着由这类鱼造成的撕裂的鳍状物。<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Kölbl-Ebert|first=Martina|last2=Ebert|first2=Martin|last3=Bellwood|first3=David R.|last4=Schulbert|first4=Christian|date=-10|title=A Piranha-like Pycnodontiform Fish from the Late Jurassic|url=https://www.cell.com/current-biology/fulltext/S0960-9822(18)31208-9|journal=Current Biology|language=en|volume=0|issue=0|doi=10.1016/j.cub.2018.09.013|issn=0960-9822|access-date=2021-02-13|archive-date=2021-01-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210102223338/https://www.cell.com/current-biology/fulltext/S0960-9822(18)31208-9|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.sci-news.com/paleontology/piranhamesodon-pinnatomus-piranha-like-teeth-fish-06520.html|title=Jurassic Flesh-Eating Fish Had Piranha-Like Teeth {{!}} Paleontology {{!}} Sci-News.com|work=Breaking Science News {{!}} Sci-News.com|access-date=2018-10-24|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108111233/http://www.sci-news.com/paleontology/piranhamesodon-pinnatomus-piranha-like-teeth-fish-06520.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-science-piranha/in-toothy-prequel-piranha-like-fish-menaced-jurassic-seas-idUSKCN1MS2Y6|title=In toothy prequel, piranha-like fish menaced Jurassic seas|last=Dunham|first=Will|work=U.S.|access-date=2018-10-24|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109032016/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-science-piranha/in-toothy-prequel-piranha-like-fish-menaced-jurassic-seas-idUSKCN1MS2Y6|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.sciencemag.org/news/2018/10/piranhalike-teeth-and-torn-fins-reveal